        },
        "text_NfiRgK": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We believe a good night’s sleep starts with high-quality materials. That’s why our mattresses are made to meet rigorous safety and emissions standards, giving parents confidence in their child’s sleep environment.\n</p><p>We are proudly certified by CertiPUR-US® and GreenGuard Gold, along with many other leading organizations, ensuring the highest standards of quality and sustainability.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><b>CertiPUR-US® Certified</b></li>\n<p>Our foams are made without ozone depleters, PBDE flame retardants, mercury, lead, and other heavy metals. These certifications ensure low emissions for better indoor air quality.</p>\n\n<li><b>GreenGuard Gold Certified</b></li>\n<p>While some mattresses rely on fiberglass as a fire barrier, ours don’t. We use safe, high-quality alternative materials that meet all safety standards—no fiberglass, no worries!</p>\n<li><b>OEKO-TEX ®Certification</b></li>\n<p>All of our fabrics are OEKO-TEX® certified and tested to be free from many harmful substances, including formaldehyde and heavy metals like cadmium and nickel, meeting strict U.S. and European standards.</p>\n</ul>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
