        "text_jLcixe": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The ultimate sleep setup for kids, our CertiPUR-US® certified Memory Foam Mattress + Bedding Bundle offers pressure relief and optimal support for growing bodies. Its water resistant 100% organic cotton cover zips off, making cleaning a breeze. The mattress features a cooling layer (say goodbye to night sweats) adapting to your child's temperature keeping them comfortable all night long.</p>\n\n<b>The Bedding Bundle includes:</b>\n<ul>\n<p>\n</p>\n<li>100% organic cotton sheet set for added softness\n</li>\n<li>Waterproof, machine-washable mattress protector</li>\n<li>Kid-friendly pillow(s) for proper neck support</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<p>Everything your child needs for a cozy, restful night’s sleep. Also available without bedding bundle.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
