    "iocn_text_grid_Lc6pLg": {
      "type": "iocn-text-grid",
      "blocks": {
        "icon_text_grid_By8U3m": {
          "type": "icon_text_grid",
          "settings": {
            "icon_image": "shopify://shop_images/challenge.png",
            "icon_text": "The Challenge",
            "icon_description": "<p>Study after study proves the importance of good rest for child development. But before we created 5 Little Monkeys, we couldn’t find a sleep system with children’s needs in mind. No one seemed to consider the important differences between grown-up bodies and growing bodies – or how kids sleep would be affected by those differences.</p>"
          }
        },
        "icon_text_grid_KgK3YE": {
          "type": "icon_text_grid",
          "settings": {
            "icon_image": "shopify://shop_images/thoughtful_design.png",
            "icon_text": "Thoughtful Design",
            "icon_description": "<p>We set out to create a brand new kind of toddler mattress that can be used from age 3 through age 18. We started from the ground up, working to address a range of concerns in the design process like:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Body weight and proportions</li>\n<li>Changing body structure</li>\n<li>Body temperature regulation</li>\n<li>Tendency to have nighttime \"accidents\"</li>\n<li>Allergies</li>\n</ul>"
          }
        },
        "icon_text_grid_GqKfxq": {
          "type": "icon_text_grid",
          "settings": {
            "icon_image": "shopify://shop_images/solution_crib_to_college.png",
            "icon_text": "A Solution From Crib To College",
            "icon_description": "<p>We created 5 Little Monkeys specifically for growing kids. We researched, studied and designed the optimum features and benefits to support better sleep in children. Then, we created an entire sleep system bed incorporating the very best of our findings. That means, not only is the 5 Little Monkeys Mattress the best choice for your growing monkeys, it’s the last one you’ll ever have to buy them! Our sleep system bed is the perfect toddler mattress that your child can transition to from the crib and continue to sleep in throughout their teenage years.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
